<!-- ================= COVER ================= -->
<div class="cover">
<div class="kicker">NAMAN SHARMA IAS ACADEMY</div>
<div class="title">NAMANIAS.COM</div>
<div class="sub">Web Portal — Staff Operations Manual</div>
<p style="margin-top:24pt; color:#3b4452; font-size:12pt;">The official, complete, role-by-role handbook for running the admin portal.<br/>Written so any team member with basic computer skills can follow every step with confidence.</p>
<div class="meta">
<b>Document:</b> NAMAN-IAS-WEB-PORTAL-MANUAL.doc<br/>
<b>Audience:</b> All portal staff (Course, Content, Webinar, Payment, Finance, Support, Admin)<br/>
<b>Base address:</b> https://namanias.com<br/>
