<h2>(b) Topics requested but NOT in the codebase (real gaps)</h2>
<ul>
<li><b>Self-service "Forgot password" for admins</b> — not implemented. Reset is manager-driven via Staff &amp; Roles → Manage → Reset password.</li>
<li><b>Clone/duplicate a whole COURSE</b> — not implemented at course level. You can <b>Duplicate</b> a <b>batch</b> within a course and use <b>Quick add combinations</b>; webinars (not courses) have a full Duplicate.</li>
<li><b>Reorder webinars</b> — not implemented (only courses can be drag-reordered).</li>
<li><b>Named "free preview" toggle per lecture</b> — not a separate toggle. The equivalent is a hosted video's <b>Visibility = Public</b>.</li>
<li><b>Gateway refund processing</b> — not implemented. Only a <b>Refunded</b> status can be set (Super Admin); the actual money refund is done in the payment gateway.</li>
<li><b>Per-course SEO is present</b>, but a standalone global SEO manager beyond per-item SEO tabs is not part of these procedures.</li>
</ul>

<h2>(c) Capabilities found in the code that staff should know (not originally listed)</h2>
<ul>
<li><b>Re-verify payments with the bank (ICICI)</b> — all/filtered/single, never downgrades PAID.</li>
<li><b>Payment Trash</b> with Restore and permanent delete (Super Admin), plus full lifecycle history per payment.</li>
<li><b>Duplicate-payment detection</b> and <b>Mark others superseded</b> for clean paid groups.</li>
<li><b>Abandoned-checkout "hot leads"</b> with Call / WhatsApp / SMS / Verify.</li>
<li><b>Move late registrations</b> between webinars; <b>Duplicate webinar</b> ("mark old ended" + link).</li>
<li><b>Staff comp access</b> (Grant access / Bulk enroll) and a <b>student-portal test login</b> (phone + login code) — never counted as revenue.</li>
<li><b>Orientation/starter video reuse</b> across many courses/webinars from one upload.</li>
<li><b>Access at Risk</b> recovery (grant +1 month / Lifetime / Revoke) and per-student <b>Access control</b> (validity presets, custom date, +30 days, revoke/restore, access history).</li>
<li><b>Student profile analytics</b>: customer journey timeline, test performance, receipts (PDF download), payments ledger.</li>
<li><b>Sync paying students</b> button to pull online/offline payers into the list.</li>
<li><b>Change plan / Manage installments</b> (waive, cancel, edit due dates) on a student's course.</li>
<li><b>CSV export</b> of payments (respects filters).</li>
<li><b>Whole modules</b> also available to the right roles: Lead CRM, Lead Forms, Landing Pages, Marketing, Referrals, SMS Mission Control, Quizzes/Question Bank/Imports, Current Affairs (articles, daily, PDFs, analytics), Toppers, Home/About/Navigation, Subscription Plans, Lecture Q&amp;A.</li>
</ul>

